description:
Watch as the story of the flood from Genesis chapters 8 and 9 comes to life in iBIBLE—the world’s first visual and interactive Bible. After the rain stopped on the earth, God told Noah, his family, and all the animals to come out from the ark. Then, God makes a promise to Noah and all of creation that He will never flood the earth again, and He sets a rainbow in the clouds as a sign of His promise. Study the Biblical Narrative and enjoy this presentation of God’s Word with iBIBLE.

A production of RevelationMedia, iBIBLE brings God’s Word to life in a format that people all over the world can engage with. Through dramatic audio and vibrant animation, people of all ages, all backgrounds, and with all abilities can learn the Biblical Narrative—the one cohesive story of Scripture. iBIBLE will be available for free to translate into any of the world’s 7,000+ languages. Join the movement today and help bring the true story of God’s Word to the nations for free!

Visit www.iBIBLE.app to see all completed episodes of iBIBLE—a visual Bible for a visual and connected world! 

Director: Steve Cleary
